  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>How often can I upload files?</strong>
    <ul>
      You can upload files as often as you like.  If your inventory has not changed, the software will inform you that
      0 items have changed.
      
      I recommend uploading when initially setting up your optimizer account
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>What if the software reports that it didn't know about an item?</strong>
    <ul>
      This can occur due to a mis-spelling of the existing data or it could be a new item which was recently added to the
      game and has not been added yet to the optimizer. I am notified if this occurs.
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>What if the software updates my inventory incorrectly?</strong>
    <ul>
      This can occur due to a change in the format of the downloaded file.  I am not a Castle Age developer and they may make
      changes as they see fit.  If this occurs, you can email me, and I'll attempt to fix the feature as soon as I am able.  To
      fix the error, you may update the inventory manually.  <%= link_to 'Contact the Admin', 'mailto:larsonm@msu.edu' %>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>